Paper: hep-th/9711111

Date: 1997-11-17

Title: Gravitationally dressed Parke-Taylor amplitudes

Authors: K.Selivanov

Comments: 4 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A12 (1997) 3087-3090

A generating function for the Parke-Taylor amplitudes with any number ofpositive helicity gravitons in addition to the positive helicity gluons isobtained using the recently constructed self-dual classical solution of thetype of perturbiner in Yang-Mills theory interacting with gravity.